title: 'Good product'
body: I absolutely like this jacket! The quality is out good and the design is stylish and versatile. It keeps me warm during chilly days without feeling bulky. The attention to detail is evident, and the stitching is top-notch. I appreciate the functional pockets and the smooth zipper. It's become my go-to jacket for any occasion but in rainy season it's not so good. In this price it's okay to buy.
